messages.message: After downtime this afternoon (deployment, I imagine), AI Hub said I used all my credits and won’t let me do anything. I can’t imagine I actually used that many credits, so I thought I’d drop that in here. Maybe it used them up trying to load during the deployment or something?

Hmm. Can you go check this in your usage history page? Curious to see your activity which consumed $25 of credits. In general, advanced model in Converse or extracting lot of fields in Build exhausts credits much faster.
